The '''Abu Dhabi Science Festival''' is a [[science festival]] organized by the Abu Dhabi Technology Committee (TDC) which takes place annually in [[Abu Dhabi]], [[UAE]].<ref name="source1">{{cite web|url=http://www.abudhabisciencefestival.ae/the-festival/festival-info |title=Festival Info |publisher=Abu Dhabi Science Festival Website |date= September 2013}}</ref> The festival features lots of exhibitions, workshops, shows and signature events, as well as school tours for children around the city.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.thinkflash.ae/events/abu-dhabi-science-festival-2013 |title=Abu Dhabi Science Festival 2013 |publisher=Thinkflash.ae |date= |accessdate=2014-06-24}}</ref> The festival was first held in 2011, and its sponsors and partners are [[Edinburgh Science Festival]], [[Tawazun]], [[Dolphin Energy]], [[ADNOC]], [[Etihad Airways]], [[Masdar]], Total, [[ADEC]], Abu Dhabi Municipality, [[OSN]], Radio 2, [[Abu Dhabi Media]], Ferrari World, and produced by Flash Entertainment.<ref name="source1" />
In 2013, the festival moved to a bigger location at the du Forum [[Yas Island]] and the Abu Dhabi Corniche East Plaza, as well as reaching new locations in the UAE<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sciencefestival.co.uk/news/everyday/abu-dhabi-science-festival-launches-1794 |title=Abu Dhabi Science Festival Launches |publisher=Edinburgh International Science Festival |date=2013-09-24 |accessdate=2014-06-24}}</ref> with a regional tour that will showcase events across the Northern Emirates including [[Ras Al Khaimah]], [[Fujairah]] and [[Umm Al Quwain]] <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/uae/science/abu-dhabi-science-festival-to-visit-northern-emirates |first=Vesela |last=Todorova |title=Abu Dhabi Science Festival to visit northern emirates|work=The National |publisher=Thenational.ae |date=October 9, 2013 |accessdate=2014-06-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/uae/science/abu-dhabi-science-festival-draws-on-international-attractions|title=Abu Dhabi Science Festival draws on international attractions|last=Croucher|first=Martin|date=October 29, 2013|work=The National|accessdate=24 June 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/uae/education/all-systems-go-for-abu-dhabi-science-festival | title= All systems go for Abu Dhabi Science Festival|work=The National |date=November 7, 2013 |accessdate=2014-06-24}}</ref>
